Dialogue: 0,00:21:21.44,00:21:23.69,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为何还没入睡
Dialogue: 0,00:21:23.74,00:21:26.32,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在这糟糕的日子 听着"Bye Bye Black Birds"
Dialogue: 0,00:21:26.45,00:21:30.16,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自言自语也无法消除不安
Dialogue: 0,00:21:30.95,00:21:32.79,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}最近几个小时
Dialogue: 0,00:21:32.95,00:21:36.08,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我总是不断哭泣  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,00:21:37.54,00:21:40.75,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望你在这里
Dialogue: 0,00:21:42.92,00:21:47.47,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看你给我的那些信
Dialogue: 0,00:21:47.55,00:21:53.35,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每读一遍  痛苦都会消失
Dialogue: 0,00:21:53.68,00:21:56.60,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不会孤单
Dialogue: 0,00:21:56.81,00:21:59.40,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们四人在一起
Dialogue: 0,00:21:59.61,00:22:05.61,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就算离别也不能拆散我们  相信着你
Dialogue: 0,00:22:05.90,00:22:11.78,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在我身边
Dialogue: 0,00:22:11.95,00:22:16.58,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}靠近我  为你送上一颗四叶草
Dialogue: 0,00:22:16.79,00:22:18.37,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,00:22:18.37,00:22:21.13,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道你不会孤单
Dialogue: 0,00:22:21.42,00:22:24.13,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们四人在一起
Dialogue: 0,00:22:24.26,00:22:30.30,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就算离别也不能拆散我们  你就在我心中
Dialogue: 0,00:22:30.51,00:22:36.35,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为我一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,00:22:36.52,00:22:41.19,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}靠近我  为你送上一颗四叶草
Dialogue: 0,00:22:41.40,00:22:43.52,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,00:02:01.42,00:02:06.76,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}指引着我  前往远方
Dialogue: 0,00:02:06.96,00:02:15.15,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一路披荆斩棘  杀出血路
Dialogue: 0,00:02:17.39,00:02:20.33,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yo guess who’s back Everybody get down
Dialogue: 0,00:02:20.40,00:02:23.13,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}guess who’s back hey step up step up!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:33.88,00:02:38.22,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被命运捉弄  I’m falling down
Dialogue: 0,00:02:38.49,00:02:43.62,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你同奏的和声  再也不会响起
Dialogue: 0,00:02:43.69,00:02:48.82,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你强烈的香气还在心头萦绕
Dialogue: 0,00:02:49.60,00:02:51.95,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不愿再继续等待
Dialogue: 0,00:02:53.42,00:02:55.17,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hey guess who’s back
Dialogue: 0,00:02:55.50,00:02:58.79,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}带着愿望
Dialogue: 0,00:02:58.79,00:03:00.54,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)} guess who’s back
Dialogue: 0,00:03:00.75,00:03:04.05,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}轮盘预示着明天
Dialogue: 0,00:03:04.05,00:03:05.69,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)} guess who’s back
Dialogue: 0,00:03:05.96,00:03:09.33,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}点亮明灯
Dialogue: 0,00:03:09.33,00:03:10.93,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)} guess who’s back
